544
00:29:41,162 --> 00:29:43,544
I got to call Martha.

545
00:29:43,578 --> 00:29:45,477
- Wife? Girlfriend?
- Neither.

546
00:29:45,511 --> 00:29:47,306
We take walks every morning

547
00:29:47,341 --> 00:29:50,171
