the damn sunrise.

549
00:29:53,726 --> 00:29:56,039
Not your preferred activity?

550
00:29:56,074 --> 00:29:58,110
Doc, if God wanted us
to see the sunrise,

551
00:29:58,145 --> 00:30:00,699
