Look at what we made.

607
00:33:48,863 --> 00:33:50,348
Hello.

608
00:33:50,382 --> 00:33:52,591
It is very nice to meet you.

609
00:33:53,937 --> 00:33:55,801
I am Dr. Shaun Murphy.

610
00:33:59,770 --> 00:34:01,152
I'm your dad.

611
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:14,268
